<html>
  <head>
    <title>The org.infogrid.util.event package</title>
  </head>
  <body>
  <p>A better event framework than <code>java.util.EventObject</code>. In particular,
     this package provides the framework for creating events that serialize well.
     For compatibility, {@link org.infogrid.util.event.ExternalizableEvent} does attempt to inherit from
     <code>java.util.EventObject</code>.</p>
  </body>
</html>
